Class SlowPduSender

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.sii.ogham.testing.sms.simulator.jsmpp.SlowPduSender
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.jsmpp.PDUSender

    public class SlowPduSender
extends Object
implements org.jsmpp.PDUSender
    Decorate a real PDUSender. If delay is configured, it waits for that delay before sending the real PDU.
